{"tid":1727090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"〖美國戰線眾籌〗HKDC遊說團要大家課金呀！！沈旭輝認證團隊！！","createTime":"2019-11-16T10:25:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T06:41:17.000Z","uid":37688,"like":81,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"80def0db853e0d2cfcf2f16d5ad233004c9caac3","tid":1727090,"uid":37688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:25:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">想講係US DC一直都有依個海外港人組成既遊說團 <br />\n但見好似完全無人提過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實香港真係好需要組成一個長駐美國既遊說團，<br />\n因為中共都有做緊反遊說<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家除咗捐錢比星火，612之外都可唔支持下佢地</span><br />\n人哋默默耕耘咗幾年，無理由唔捐錢幫手！！！<br />\n<br />\nFrom 沈旭輝 FB:<br />\n🇺🇸 關於美國《香港人權與民主法案》的來龍去脈，香港人怎樣在背後lobby，是一段鮮為人知的故事，知道了曾經幫手手足的參與，會感到香港未來充滿希望。HKDC是為了集中推動法案而成立的組織，負責人Samuel（左二）是極少數香港出生的專業lobbyist，假如這方面的工作日後能專業培訓新一代，香港人的國際能量會源源不絕釋放。原來Samuel就是朱耀明牧師的公子；身旁Emily曾是我的員工，現於DC為港人事務奔走；另一位Simon則是中學師弟，先於Delaware定居。<br />\n而我純粹是訪客，知道了這幾年所有人的辛勞，感觸良多。<br />\n大家最關心的「法案幾時通過」問題：現在參議院的hotline process不成文慣例是一個工作天，週末放假後復會的星期一，根據Senator Rubio和DC4HK的資訊，應該有好消息。<br />\n<br />\nHKDC FB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkdc.us/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkdc.us%2F&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQHyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=1a6fac3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkdc.us/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">眾籌LINK: </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><a href=\"https://www.gofundme.com/f/US4HK?utm_source=customer&amp;utm_medium=copy_link&amp;utm_campaign=p_cp+share-sheet\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gofundme.com%2Ff%2FUS4HK%3Futm_source%3Dcustomer%26utm_medium%3Dcopy_link%26utm_campaign%3Dp_cp%2Bshare-sheet&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQHyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=70f26eb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gofundme.com/f/US4HK?utm_source=customer&amp;utm_medium=copy_link&amp;utm_campaign=p_cp+share-sheet</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"2255312402b68474c1d1844fd599232e5465c2c3","tid":1727090,"uid":37688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:26:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"17eb88468ee5284dd2d54de84ae4cc312d4d222a","tid":1727090,"uid":37688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:26:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db58e9899b95440389594ec9834d301437a912a2","tid":1727090,"uid":37688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:27:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d7e14bf7ef7e9cc3f9745d1c53bdb0ba2f3c3421","tid":1727090,"uid":37688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:27:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b30eaaab2c2f98807e91c62b4d8e60494d322a0","tid":1727090,"uid":37688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:27:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3dc7e09eff2809dbb24b1a264d9cc4c083c0f719","tid":1727090,"uid":104165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:27:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9184593b7efcfb246b9f624bf72b874ec6c71019","tid":1727090,"uid":74432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:27:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"45efb3782c188f8de35a62e48915d4b4c5ffdc31","tid":1727090,"uid":37688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:27:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d12111fca593974573cb1da449c714b2b190af06","tid":1727090,"uid":37688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:28:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f44f9396a6bd44fe2f999b03963d27a57df0595e","tid":1727090,"uid":285371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:28:23.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"5cd7dc871c9186909c47d993a3473b68e056f56b","tid":1727090,"uid":37688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:28:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c8ace131f87dec1ae7