\n本地藍屍撐由佢地，佢係係咪都奶共架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好大件事 唔好玩膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國國會美中經濟與安全審議委員會發表年度報告，表示若果中國對香港出動解放軍或武警干預香港局勢，美國國會應該撤銷《美國-香港政策法》給予香港獨立關稅區的特殊地位。"},{"pid":"0e5315263caee88068b76431e23dede4a82bc1de","tid":1727090,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:35:11.000Z","msg":"Mk輝認證先危險<br />\n仲要兩個係佢既人<br />\n<br />\n佢係紅底<br />\n雖然最近出文正常"},{"pid":"0a975b37aac7fccc29784fd34d2ec036c943d1b3","tid":1727090,"uid":113148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:37:41.000Z","msg":"對唔住負錯皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推返"},{"pid":"ceaa011706f5c82d5956f3b3283b5c0bc591ecd2","tid":1727090,"uid":37688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:38:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d285c169faa9e9ad22d216237b5bfec604c99182","tid":1727090,"uid":37688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:41:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5ee2789b7feb17020289e4ad4d766a5f2f12977c","tid":1727090,"uid":37688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e5315263caee88068b76431e23dede4a82bc1de","tid":1727090,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:35:11.000Z","msg":"Mk輝認證先危險<br />\n仲要兩個係佢既人<br />\n<br />\n佢係紅底<br />\n雖然最近出文正常"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:44:14.000Z","msg":"依家講野黃到咁都紅底？<br />\n你睇開佢fb就知佢痴咗線"},{"pid":"4a98f82b61e634980901479a28b1ffcbdf8b66ab","tid":1727090,"uid":37688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:44:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7da46f2010b3d44d71ef87b2b81c297d3a034fd3","tid":1727090,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:44:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/p