mal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:57:15.000Z","msg":"國際關係學者佢算數一數二 而且network肯定好過好多人啦"},{"pid":"48675537e305dcdbfd98750a1238436d4ba12e70","tid":1727090,"uid":37688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:59:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"debdde1fc745bfdf17e4e5f0d4d966dde94a1a28","tid":1727090,"uid":195187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80def0db853e0d2cfcf2f16d5ad233004c9caac3","tid":1727090,"uid":37688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:25:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">想講係US DC一直都有依個海外港人組成既遊說團 <br />\n但見好似完全無人提過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實香港真係好需要組成一個長駐美國既遊說團，<br />\n因為中共都有做緊反遊說<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家除咗捐錢比星火，612之外都可唔支持下佢地</span><br />\n人哋默默耕耘咗幾年，無理由唔捐錢幫手！！！<br />\n<br />\nFrom 沈旭輝 FB:<br />\n🇺🇸 關於美國《香港人權與民主法案》的來龍去脈，香港人怎樣在背後lobby，是一段鮮為人知的故事，知道了曾經幫手手足的參與，會感到香港未來充滿希望。HKDC是為了集中推動法案而成立的組織，負責人Samuel（左二）是極少數香港出生的專業lobbyist，假如這方面的工作日後能專業培訓新一代，香港人的國際能量會源源不絕釋放。原來Samuel就是朱耀明牧師的公子；身旁Emily曾是我的員工，現於DC為港人事務奔走；另一位Simon則是中學師弟，先於Delaware定居。<br />\n而我純粹是訪客，知道了這幾年所有人的辛勞，感觸良多。<br />\n大家最關心的「法案幾時通過」問題：現在參議院的hotline process不成文慣例是一個工作天，週末放假後復會的星期一，根據Senator Rubio和DC4HK的資訊，應該有好消息。<br />\n<br />\nHKDC FB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkdc.us/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkdc.us%2F&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQHyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=1a6fac3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkdc.us/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">眾籌LINK: </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><a href=\"https://www.gofundme.com/f/US4HK?utm_source=customer&amp;utm_medium=copy_link&amp;utm_campaign=p_cp+share-sheet\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gofundme.com%2Ff%2FUS4HK%3Futm_source%3Dcustomer%26utm_medium%3Dcopy_link%26utm_campaign%3Dp_